<v-layout align-center justify-center row wrap>
  <v-flex xs12>
    <v-alert type="info" :value="!!output">
      {{output}}
    </v-alert>
  </v-flex>

  <v-flex sm4 lg3>
    <login-form :status="loginStatus" @submit="login" autofocus />
  </v-flex>
  <v-flex sm4 lg3>
    <registration-form :status="registrationStatus" @submit="register" />
  </v-flex>
  <v-flex sm4 lg3>
    <forgot-password-form :status="forgotPasswordStatus" @submit="sendForgotPasswordEmail" />
  </v-flex>
  <v-flex sm4 lg3>
    <router-link
        v-if="!$route.query['reset-password-token']"
        :to="{query: { 'reset-password-token': 'dummy-token-value' }}"
        class="d-block text-xs-right mb-5"
    >
      Set fake token in URL
    </router-link>
    <reset-password-form :status="resetPasswordStatus" @submit="resetPassword" />
  </v-flex>

  <v-flex sm4 lg3>
    <login-card />
  </v-flex>
  <v-flex sm4 lg3>
    <registration-card />
  </v-flex>
  <v-flex sm4 lg3>
    <forgot-password-card />
  </v-flex>
  <v-flex sm4 lg3>
    <reset-password-card />
  </v-flex>
</v-layout>
